snippet.title: Rayman Legends Definitive Edition Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Get ready to rock your Nintendo Switch with Rayman Legends Definitive Edition, which contains the critically acclaimed game Rayman Legends as well as new exclusive features. Rayman and his friends must run, jump, and fight their way through colorful, mythical worlds in this platforming adventure.

Rayman Legends Definitive Edition is Available Now! https://goo.gl/24XvgL

#NintendoSwitch #Rayman #RaymanLegendsDefinitiveEdition
